import sys
input=sys.stdin.readline
n=int(input())
L=list(map(int,input().split()))
q=int(input())
ct2=0
ct4=0
ct6=0
ct8=0
ct=[0]*(10**5+10)
for i in L:ct[i]+=1
for i in ct:
    if i>1:ct2+=1
    if i>3:ct4+=1
    if i>5:ct6+=1
    if i>7:ct8+=1
for i in ' '*q:
    a,b=input().split()
    b=int(b)
    if a=='+':
        ct[b]+=1
        if ct[b]==2:ct2+=1
        if ct[b]==4:ct4+=1
        if ct[b]==6:ct6+=1
        if ct[b]==8:ct8+=1
    else:
        ct[b]-=1
        if ct[b]==1:ct2-=1
        if ct[b]==3:ct4-=1
        if ct[b]==5:ct6-=1
        if ct[b]==7:ct8-=1
    if ct2>=2 and ct6>=1:print('YES')
    elif ct2>=3 and ct4>=1:print('YES')
    elif ct4>=2:print('YES')
    elif ct8:print('YES')
    else:print('NO')
